race.description: The Star Gold Coast Magic Millions The Debut Plate
race.comment: The $500,000 The Debut. The well-bred LADY MOSCATO (6) (dam was a G2 winner and G1 placed) has looked super impressive winning both Sydney trials and is sure to be well-educated out of the Waterhouse/Bott yard. Hoop King has been in the saddle for both hit outs to date and sticks here for race day. Ready to fire on debut. TOORAK JEWEL (7) was a dominant ten-length Gold Coast trial winner and gets the services of champion jockey J Mac in the saddle. Include in calculations. WENDELL (4) is another to show ability in a Rosehill trial and a strong debut effort would not surprise. PROFIT IN PARADISE (2) gets Rodd on board from a low draw and can make his presence felt. DOLLY BOOM (5) is out of a Listed winner and gets the Gollan polish. Keep safe.
